original_text: Mathematical aspects of computer-aided share trading We consider problems of statistical analysis of share prices and propose probabilistic characteristics to describe the price series. We discuss three methods of mathematical modelling of price series with given probabilistic characteristics

Discutimos tres métodos de modelización matemática de series de precios con características probabilísticas dadas
